Package: caja-wipe
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         libgsecuredelete0,
         libgtk-3-0,
         libcaja-extension1
Description: Secure deletion extension for Caja
 Caja Wipe is a Caja extension that adds "Securely erase" and
 "Securely fill empty space" items to the right-click menu.
 .
 The progress and results of the operations are shown in a progress
 dialog.
